{"type": "article", "id": 21047, "title": "带小装饰的镜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-21T07:24:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141417xtyFXisqj9YQOcvS.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙的设计工作室 kutarq studio 最近推出的是这组镜子，主体是圆形或者长方形的。特别在于在镜子的边缘增加了一些点缀，包括 4 种圆形或方形的彩色夹子和一根绳子，可以随意组合并调整位置。看似简单的改变却打破了镜子原有的冰冷感，瞬间生动起来，很有趣味。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150721LpFZB9520kQK7YUW.gif\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150725TASRj8cOdMCyv62f.gif\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150726SwHGz1NbLu5CEohX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150727kDCsoPM3iwd6uUmA.gif\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}